name: Modern Holiday 10 pk - Mod Tree
description:
These simple but elegant Christmas Tree cards are a great way to stay in contact with friends and family during the holiday season.

The front greeting can be changed to anything you like...
Merry Christmas, Season's Greetings, Happy Holidays, and so on...

The inside text is customized per your request, or I can leave the name part blank for you to sign by hand.

This listing is for a set of 10 cards with white envelopes.
Cards are 5.5" wide by 4" high, folded.

Cards a designed by Susana Ortiz of Sanctum Design Studio and professionally printed.

Please order by December 10 to get them by Christmas.
